 \begin{pmatrix}-1\\3\\0\end{pmatrix}- \begin{pmatrix}1\\-2\\0\end{pmatrix}= \begin{pmatrix}-2\\5\\0\end{pmatrix} \qquad \begin{pmatrix}3\\-2\\1\end{pmatrix} 
