n
\frac{\begin{pmatrix}5\\2\\-11\end{pmatrix}\cdot \begin{pmatrix}-1\\3\\0\end{pmatrix}} {\sqrt{\begin{pmatrix}5\\2\\-11\end{pmatrix}\cdot \begin{pmatrix}5\\2\\-11\end{pmatrix}}} = \frac{-5+6}{\sqrt{25+4+121}}=\frac{1}{5\sqrt6}
